ref: https://cococubed.com/code_pages/ppm_1d.shtml
The tool ppm.tbz is a simplified 1D PPM hydrodynamics solver on Cartesian grids. This tool is originally from Bruce Fryxell.

compile, with say

% ifort ppm.f90 -o ppm.exe

run the executable

% ./ppm.exe 
    1  0.00E+00  1.20E-03
